Description: desktop satellite tracking and orbital analysis for amateur radio
 OrbitDeck is a desktop application for satellite tracking and orbital
 analysis, built for amateur-radio operators who work the birds. It provides
 live look angles, sky and ground tracks, pass prediction, Doppler and
 link-budget tools, an interactive and printable OSCARLOCATOR, illumination
 and mutual-window analysis, and a built-in classroom of orbital-mechanics
 explainers.
 .
 Radio (CAT) and rotator control are intentionally out of scope, since
 excellent dedicated tools already cover those.
